# Naomi Was Here This is just an example of what a blog post might look like. ## This is a sub-heading... ### And here's some other cool stuff: Here's some code, `
`, between 2 backticks. ````js // this is multi-line code: function anotherExample(firstLine, lastLine) { if (firstLine == "```" && lastLine == "```") { return multiLineCode; } } ```` You can also make text **bold**... whoa! Or _italic_. Or... wait for it... **_both!_** And feel free to go crazy ~~crossing stuff out~~. There's also [links](https://www.freecodecamp.org), and > Block Quotes! And if you want to get really crazy, even tables: | Wild Header | Crazy Header | Another Header? | | ---------------- | --------------- | ------------------ | | Your content can | be here, and it | can be here.... | | And here. | Okay. | I think we get it. | - And of course there are lists. - Some are bulleted. - With different indentation levels. - That look like this. 1. And there are numbered lists too. 1. Use just 1s if you want! 1.
